4. Generating the Data Encryption Configuration and Key

a. Generate an encryption key:
# export ENCRYPTION_KEY=$(head -c 32 /dev/urandom | base64)
# echo $ENCRYPTION_KEY=2j8U3JDE01jFka4n4Wn3YicVzodfsvIedwhf6c9+Ams==

Create the encryption-config.yaml encryption configuration file
# envsubst < configs/encryption-config.yaml > encryption-config.yaml

